---
title: Baked Salmon and Creamy Chive Sauce with Roasted Potatoes and Garlicky Green Beans
description: This Baked Salmon and Creamy Chive Sauce is a crowd pleaser and is one to get the family round the dinner table for. Super simple to make, and easily customised to suit the kids too.
